.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-TAG-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-tag-list \- list distinct tags used in the wallet ledger
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-tag-list
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns all distinct non-empty tag values from the wallet's ledger table.
.PP
Output: JSON array of tag strings.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-history-export (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-ledger-add (1)
